### Create Item
POST {{url}}/createItem
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "name": "Test Product3",
  "sku": "TP-003",
  "description": "A sample product for testing.",
  "type": "goods",
  "category": "68886908b00942cf8b0b0682",
